Yes, brother.

24:03.776 --> 24:05.811
Wow.
Whoo!

24:05.811 --> 24:06.912
[ Corcoran laughs ]

24:06.912 --> 24:08.447
Incredible.

24:08.447 --> 24:09.448
Thank you.

24:09.448 --> 24:11.150
I am so cold.

24:11.150 --> 24:13.319
Guys, that was an awesome job.
Awesome job.

24:13.319 --> 24:14.687
Thank you, Robert.

24:14.687 --> 24:16.522
Congratulations, guys.
Bye, guys. Good luck.

24:16.522 --> 24:18.991
Whoo!

24:18.991 --> 24:20.926
12 months ago,
we were in my garage

24:20.926 --> 24:23.062
building cold plunges,
and now here we are.

24:23.062 --> 24:25.264
We have a deal with Robert --
$2.4 million.

24:25.264 --> 24:26.332
It's incredible.

