31:30.122 --> 31:32.991
Sharks, what is up?!

31:32.991 --> 31:34.826
My name is Seneca Hampton.

31:34.826 --> 31:36.995
I'm from
Las Vegas, Nevada, baby.

31:36.995 --> 31:38.563
Whoo! Whoo!

31:38.563 --> 31:43.368
And today I'm seeking $500,000
in exchange for 10% equity

31:43.368 --> 31:45.604
in my company,
Hampton Adams.

31:45.604 --> 31:48.440
Okay, Sharks,
if you've played sports,

31:48.440 --> 31:51.476
then you know
there is one product,

31:51.476 --> 31:52.811
one piece of equipment,

31:52.811 --> 31:55.847
