31:55.847 --> 31:58.550
Some people just
won't perform without it.

31:58.550 --> 32:00.385
Allow me to introduce you

32:00.385 --> 32:02.788
to one of the greatest creations
on planet Earth.

32:02.788 --> 32:03.922
Wow.
I present...

32:03.922 --> 32:05.757
[ Drumroll ]

32:05.757 --> 32:07.492
...athletic tape!

32:07.492 --> 32:08.827
♪ Ahhh ♪

32:08.827 --> 32:10.028
[ Laughter ]

32:10.028 --> 32:11.463
But not just any
athletic tape, Sharks.

32:11.463 --> 32:14.733
This is Hampton Adams, baby!
Whoo!

32:14.733 --> 32:17.102
Now watch this.

32:17.102 --> 32:20.138
Ugh!
It's 45 pounds here.

32:20.138 --> 32:21.973
Oh, yeah.

32:21.973 --> 32:23.875
Ah!
Greiner: Wow!

32:23.875 --> 32:25.677
-Oh!
-Whoo!

32:25.677 --> 32:27.712
-Boom!
-That is strong tape.

32:27.712 --> 32:30.048
But wait,
there's more.

32:30.048 --> 32:32.284
-Oh, there's more.
-[ Laughs ]

32:32.284 --> 32:33.785
You know that tape
that's so strong

32:33.785 --> 32:35.620
