32:37.589 --> 32:40.125
Not here, baby. We fixed that.
Watch this.

32:40.125 --> 32:41.593
♪♪

32:41.593 --> 32:42.594
Lay it like that.

32:42.594 --> 32:43.762
Ah!

32:43.762 --> 32:45.263
-What?
-It's like butter, baby.

32:45.263 --> 32:46.765
[ Laughter ]
Cuban: Like butter.

32:46.765 --> 32:48.333
By simply listening
to athletes,

32:48.333 --> 32:51.069
