light bulbs,

35:06.004 --> 35:07.772
and it was a similar model.

35:07.772 --> 35:11.676
And I just dedicated myself
and I spent 80 hours a week

35:11.676 --> 35:14.279
just working
and getting paid to learn,

35:14.279 --> 35:16.881
and I grinded it out
for three years.

35:16.881 --> 35:18.283
I said, "I think
I figured this out.

35:18.283 --> 35:19.651
I think
I know how to do it."

35:19.651 --> 35:22.253
And so I went to look
for a product for myself,

35:22.253 --> 35:23.588
and I grew up
playing football.

35:23.588 --> 35:25.590
And so I've used
a lot of athletic tape.

35:25.590 --> 35:27.459
I wanted to learn
how to become wealthy.

35:27.459 --> 35:28.727
How do I build wealth?

35:28.727 --> 35:30.261
If you knew where I came from,
you'd be like,

35:30.261 --> 35:32.130
"There's no reason you should be
standing here right now."

35:32.130 --> 35:33.598
Where did you come from?

35:33.598 --> 35:36.534
So I'm from L. A. originally,

35:36.534 --> 35:39.404
and I have four brothers,
four sisters,

35:39.404 --> 35:42.474
and there were days
where we'd go to Burger King,

35:42.474 --> 35:44.843
grab a $1 burger,
slice it in four,

35:44.843 --> 35:46.344
and that was dinner.

35:46.344 --> 35:49.180
We grew up like that --
motels, sleeping out of cars,

35:49.180 --> 35:51.883
and I was just like,
"This ain't it."

35:51.883 --> 35:53.852
And as I got older, I was like,
"You know what?

35:53.852 --> 35:55.954
I'm gonna dedicate myself
to figuring this out."

35:55.954 --> 35:58.423
And so I learned --
you build wealth,

35:58.423 --> 35:59.758
start a business.

35:59.758 --> 36:01.793
To start a business,
you need to sell your product.

36:01.793 --> 36:02.994
And so I learned sales.

36:02.994 --> 36:05.196
So what do you need
the $500,000 for?

36:05.196 --> 36:07.399
It's a cash-flow business,
and so my orders --

36:07.399 --> 36:10.035
I don't order one time
at the beginning of the year.

36:10.035 --> 36:12.737
I'm ordering every month and
getting shipments every month

36:12.737 --> 36:14.673
to be able to take the cash
they're giving

36:14.673 --> 36:15.807
into the next order
and the next order.

36:15.807 --> 36:17.308
You're basically
breaking even.

36:17.308 --> 36:19.577
Basically, to scale it
and grow it.
On a cash basis.

36:19.577 --> 36:21.379
Yeah.
But as long as
your sales are growing,

36:21.379 --> 36:24.115
it's like you're feeding
the dragon.
Exactly.

36:24.115 --> 36:26.284
Like, it keeps growing.
You got to keep feeding it.

36:26.284 --> 36:29.220
And so I never get out
of the spot where it's like,

36:29.220 --> 36:31.790
if something goes wrong,
this will all come tumbling.

36:31.790 --> 36:33.658
Cuban: Seneca, you know,
there's a bunch of companies

36:33.658 --> 36:35.727
buying smaller companies
and rolling them up.

36:35.727 --> 36:38.496
Has anybody approached you
to acquire you?

36:38.496 --> 36:41.766
I get I don't know how many of
those e-mails from those people.

36:41.766 --> 36:43.835
And why haven't you
pursued any of that?

36:43.835 --> 36:46.337
Because I'm on the fence of,
should I sell it

36:46.337 --> 36:48.239
or should I keep it going?
Herjavec: Yes.

36:48.239 --> 36:49.574
If I keep it going,
then --

36:49.574 --> 36:50.742
You should sell it.

36:50.742 --> 36:51.910
You think I should --
You should sell it.

36:51.910 --> 36:53.278
Wow.

36:53.278 --> 36:54.779
And I got to tell you,
I love business,

36:54.779 --> 36:56.781
and I love every business
I started.

36:56.781 --> 37:00.051
But I learned a long time ago,
the best time to sell

37:00.051 --> 37:01.753
is when you don't think
you need to sell

37:01.753 --> 37:03.855
and when you don't
need the money.
Amen.

37:03.855 --> 37:06.391
You're kind of on the verge
of that, honestly.
Yeah. Yeah.

37:06.391 --> 37:08.793
If you actually get
much more successful,

37:08.793 --> 37:11.362
your cash problem
may actually get much worse.

37:11.362 --> 37:13.765
Yeah.
Yeah, and if you have
to stress every month

37:13.765 --> 37:17.235
about that next month,
it's time to sell, right?
Yeah.

37:17.235 --> 37:19.971
Good advice.
But the good news is,
whatever you get for it,

37:19.971 --> 37:21.573
now you've got
the formula.

37:21.573 --> 37:23.541
I got a question.

37:23.541 --> 37:25.310
Robert, would you buy it?

37:25.310 --> 37:26.644
