38:03.581 --> 38:05.150
Robert, would you buy it?

38:05.150 --> 38:06.518
[ Laughter ]

38:06.518 --> 38:08.987
Would I buy the tape?
Would you buy the business?

38:08.987 --> 38:11.589
♪♪

38:11.589 --> 38:12.991
I love the business.

38:12.991 --> 38:15.493
I'm not gonna give you
the premium price for it.

38:15.493 --> 38:17.662
You're the right guy.

38:17.662 --> 38:19.497
You're gonna
do this again.
Thank you.

38:19.497 --> 38:21.866
Look, I'm not going to invest
'cause you --

38:21.866 --> 38:23.601
you should sell
this business.

38:23.601 --> 38:25.203
Thank you.
You've done it.
You've proven it.

38:25.203 --> 38:29.007
And like Mark said, use your
knowledge for the next one.

38:29.007 --> 38:30.642
Okay. Thank you.
Congratulations.

38:30.642 --> 38:32.277
Thank you.
I'm out.

38:32.277 --> 38:33.978
Thank you so much.
Yeah.

38:33.978 --> 38:35.847
So when you sell this,
will you come work for me?

38:35.847 --> 38:37.348
[ Laughter ]

38:37.348 --> 38:39.684
If you'll have me,
I'll do it, sure.

38:39.684 --> 38:42.620
Look, Seneca, what you've
accomplished is <i>great.</i>

38:42.620 --> 38:44.923
You did it
the exact right way.

38:44.923 --> 38:47.625
And your problem is
you're stuck in that wheel

38:47.625 --> 38:50.161
where you just can't get off,
you know,

38:50.161 --> 38:52.430
and that means
it's not investable, right?
Okay.

38:52.430 --> 38:54.766
Because there's
no extra margin there...
Yeah.

38:54.766 --> 38:56.134
...for you to be able
to pay us back.

38:56.134 --> 38:57.335
Yeah.

38:57.335 --> 38:59.137
So for those reasons,
I'm out.

38:59.137 --> 39:01.339
Okay. Thank you.

39:01.339 --> 39:03.041
I didn't know much
about athletic tape,

39:03.041 --> 39:05.476
but it seems like the only one
I'd ever buy

39:05.476 --> 39:06.644
now going forward.
Thank you.

39:06.644 --> 39:08.046
Seems fantastic.

39:08.046 --> 39:10.648
But I don't think
it's the right investment for me

39:10.648 --> 39:12.851
because the situation,
but I wish you good luck.

39:12.851 --> 39:14.953
Thank you.
And I'm sorry, I'm out.

39:16.821 --> 39:20.291
I can distinctly remember being
21, being a diner waitress,

39:20.291 --> 39:23.928
going home to my hometown
and crying

39:23.928 --> 39:26.464
because I didn't know
what the formula was...

39:26.464 --> 39:29.000
Wow.
...for making a change.

39:29.000 --> 39:32.103
You know?
But can I tell you something?

39:32.103 --> 39:34.339
Once I decided
I was in control,

39:34.339 --> 39:37.675
that I could make a change
and the key to it was knowledge,

39:37.675 --> 39:40.645
I got really smart, really fast,
like a hungry animal.

39:40.645 --> 39:41.913
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

39:41.913 --> 39:44.449
And I don't think
people realize

39:44.449 --> 39:47.118
how much desire
has to do with success.

39:47.118 --> 39:49.954
Yeah.
And so you're the walking,
talking billboard

39:49.954 --> 39:51.656
of how to do it right.
Thank you.

39:51.656 --> 39:53.992
