I'm not investing because

39:53.992 --> 39:56.594
we'll just get in the rat mill
with you, you know what I mean?

39:56.594 --> 39:59.030
Yeah.
So I'm out.

39:59.030 --> 40:00.565
Thank you, Barbara.
Thank you.

40:00.565 --> 40:02.634
O'Leary: I think you've
achieved something

40:02.634 --> 40:03.868
that's quite impressive.

40:03.868 --> 40:06.804
But the problem,
the challenge of this deal is

40:06.804 --> 40:08.840
half a million --
how do I get it back?

40:08.840 --> 40:10.375
I don't know what
your business is worth --

40:10.375 --> 40:12.443
somewhere between
$3 million and $5 million.

40:12.443 --> 40:13.711
But I'll make you
an offer.

40:13.711 --> 40:15.847
It's the only way
I could do it.

40:15.847 --> 40:17.582
This is a classic
royalty deal

40:17.582 --> 40:20.118
because there is no other way
to get your money back.

40:20.118 --> 40:21.653
He's got 20% margins.

40:21.653 --> 40:24.055
I'll give you
the $500,000.

40:24.055 --> 40:25.723
I want
a dollar a package

40:25.723 --> 40:27.959
until I get
a million and a half back.

40:27.959 --> 40:31.496
So basically, I'm trying to make
a million off my $500,000, okay?

40:31.496 --> 40:33.431
Yeah.
You can't do that.

40:33.431 --> 40:34.732
I'll take the 10%
because you might sell it

40:34.732 --> 40:38.169
before I ever get back
my dollars, okay?

40:38.169 --> 40:40.772
I got to be honest with you.
I don't know how else to do it.

40:40.772 --> 40:42.640
Yeah. I --
Herjavec:
You can't do this deal.

40:42.640 --> 40:44.375
Seneca, you're digging
a deeper hole.

40:44.375 --> 40:46.778
Well, that's the guy
that said no to you, right?

40:46.778 --> 40:48.646
I'm gonna use
Kevin's own quote.

40:48.646 --> 40:51.482
"I forbid you
to take this deal."

40:51.482 --> 40:55.019
You are just punting
the problem forward, man.
Says the guy
who's giving you nothing.

40:55.019 --> 40:58.189
Seneca, the problem isn't
the equity or the amount.

40:58.189 --> 40:59.857
Yeah.
The problem is
the royalty

40:59.857 --> 41:01.960
'cause your margins
are so low already --

41:01.960 --> 41:03.795
Seneca,
it's great to get advice

41:03.795 --> 41:05.163
from people who are
giving you this.

41:05.163 --> 41:07.265
He's taking 7%.
It's a loan-shark deal.

41:07.265 --> 41:08.299
-Yeah.
-It really, really is.

41:08.299 --> 41:09.701
Why don't you counter him
and tell him

41:09.701 --> 41:11.436
you'll give him 10 cents?
I hear a noise, but zero.

41:11.436 --> 41:13.237
I just don't want you
to make a bad deal.

41:13.237 --> 41:15.206
Don't mistake
today's problem

41:15.206 --> 41:17.675
by replacing it
with a long-term problem.

41:17.675 --> 41:20.345
What he's offering you
<i>seems</i> good today,

41:20.345 --> 41:23.848
but it's cutting
into your margin forever.
Yeah. Yeah.

41:23.848 --> 41:27.085
No, it isn't forever. It goes
away after a million and a half.

41:27.085 --> 41:29.053
[ Laughs ] Goes away when
you're out of business

41:29.053 --> 41:30.521
because you gave away
all your margin.

41:30.521 --> 41:32.323
Well, then
I'm losing money.

41:32.323 --> 41:33.658
If you actually go
out of business, I lose money.

41:33.658 --> 41:35.059
That's a bad outcome
for me.

41:35.059 --> 41:37.362
You know, I love it
when Sharks give you advice

41:37.362 --> 41:39.163
and it's so valuable.

41:39.163 --> 41:41.899
I'm the only Shark
that believes in you --

41:41.899 --> 41:43.234
the only one.

41:43.234 --> 41:44.736
All roads lead back
to Mr. Wonderful.

41:46.804 --> 41:49.240
I appreciate the offer,

41:49.240 --> 41:50.575
but I have to pass on
the offer.

41:50.575 --> 41:52.777
I appreciate it.
Thank you very much.

41:52.777 --> 41:55.646
But I hope you come back with us
with your next great business

41:55.646 --> 41:58.149
because you are
a natural-born entrepreneur...
Thank you.

41:58.149 --> 42:00.551
...and a phenomenal symbol
of how to do it right.

42:00.551 --> 42:02.086
Thank you.
Thank you guys so much.

42:02.086 --> 42:03.187
-All right, take care.
-Good luck, Seneca.

42:03.187 --> 42:04.188
Greiner:
Good luck, Seneca.

42:05.189 --> 42:07.158
That is success.
He was amazing.

42:08.793 --> 42:10.595
Hampton: I'm gonna take
Robert's advice.

42:10.595 --> 42:12.330
I'm gonna sell the company.

42:12.330 --> 42:15.566
I didn't get a deal, but I got
something much more valuable.

42:15.566 --> 42:17.635
I got knowledge
from millionaire--

42:17.635 --> 42:19.003
multimillionaires
and billionaires,

42:19.003 --> 42:21.139
which you can't put
a price tag on.

42:21.139 --> 42:23.007
They've been through it
before you.

42:23.007 --> 42:25.410
So, to me, that's like gold.

